<div class="process">
	<h3>How I work</h3>
	<p class="subtitle">
		Commencing from the initial challenges and ensuring we address the right
		ones is crucial to ensure that we deliver effective solutions to both
		users and businesses.
	</p>

	<r-grid columns="10" class="process--list-wrapper">
		<r-cell span="5" span-s="row" class="process-card">
			<div class="thumbnail-wrapper">{% icon "observe" %}</div>

			<div class="title">
				<p class="body-large">Observe</p>
				<p class="description">
					By observing, I believe we can develop a greater
					understanding of user experience and needs by observing them
					in their natural environment.
				</p>
			</div>
		</r-cell>

		<r-cell span="5" span-s="row" class="process-card">
			<div class="thumbnail-wrapper">{% icon "reflect" %}</div>

			<div class="title">
				<p class="body-large">Reflect</p>
				<p class="description">
					Reflecting on our work, take into account different
					perspectives and be prepared to change in order to stay true
					to the team's values.
				</p>
			</div>
		</r-cell>

		<r-cell span="5" span-s="row" class="process-card">
			<div class="thumbnail-wrapper">{% icon "make" %}</div>

			<div class="title">
				<p class="body-large">Make</p>
				<p class="description">
					I work fast, like really fast. Quick iteration allows us to
					zoom through explorations until we arrive at something that
					feels just right.
				</p>
			</div>
		</r-cell>
	</r-grid>
</div>
